					<msContents class="lccn.loc.gov/n79090052" rend="visible">
						<summary>A portion of a daily prayer book.</summary>
						<textLang mainLang="he"/>
						<msItem n="0" rend="visible" class="lccn.loc.gov/n79090052">
							<locus from="1r" to="113v"/>
							<title xml:lang="en">Sidur</title>
							<title xml:lang="he">סדור</title>
							<decoNote type="border">1 full foliate border in colours. <locus n="113r"/>
							</decoNote>
							<decoNote type="marginal">8 textual drawings in the margins in brown ink. <locus n="39r, 39v, 42r, 43v, 45r, 45v, 55v, 74v"/>
							</decoNote>
							<decoNote type="initial">5 drawings of animals or dragons accompanying initial words, in ink. <locus n="3r, 37r, 45r, 53v, 63v"/>
							</decoNote>
							<decoNote type="initial">Numerous decorated initial words and initial-word panels, in sepia, violet and red ink. </decoNote>
							<decoNote type="marginal">8 marginal drawings in ink. <locus n="17r, 20v, 25r, 25v, 51v, 71r, 81r, 105r"/>
							</decoNote>
							<decoNote type="marginal">Manicula.<locus n="89v"/>
							</decoNote>
							<colophon xml:lang="he">ותשלם המלאכה [...] היום יום כ'ו' ימים לירח כסליו שנת <date calendar="Hebrew">חמשת אלפים ושלשים</date> לבריאת עולם אשר כתבתי על זאת התפלה. אני הלבלר <name type="person" role="scribe">יואל ב"ר שמעון</name> ז"ל כתבתי זאת התפלה לר' <name type="person" role="patron">מנחם בכמ"ר שמואל</name> ז"ל לו ולבתו הנכבדת והמשכל' הבתולה הנעימה מרת <name type="person" role="patron">מרוילייא</name> שתחיי' להתפלל בה היא וזרעה וזרע זרעה עד סוף. א'כ'י'ר'.   <locus n="112r"/>
							</colophon>
							<note>
								<p>The scribe gave the date erroneously as 26 Kislev 5030 [which would be 1269] instead of 5230 [1469].</p>
								<p>See further: <ref target="Davidson_1924"/> [on the text]; <ref target="JQR" type="number">27 (1937)</ref>, pp.
217-32; <ref target="St_in_Bibliography" type="number">9 (1970)</ref>, pp. 76-95; <ref target="JJA" type="number">3-4 (1977)</ref>, pp. 28-29;

<ref target="JJA" type="number">7 (1980)</ref>, pp. 25-26; <ref target="Metzger_1982" type="page">304</ref>; <ref target="Goldstein_1985" type="page">9</ref>; <ref target="Weinstein_1990" type="page">27-101</ref>; <ref target="Viator" type="number">26 (1995)</ref>, pp. 265-82; <ref target="Revue" type="number">155 (1997)</ref>, pp. 33-52; <ref target="Zucker_2005" type="page">XIII</ref>
; <ref target="Auskunft" type="number">26 (2006)</ref>, pp. 287-309.</p>
							</note>
						</msItem>
